snippet.title: Visualizing the Advanced Bullet Dynamics Trajectory - Weapons Simulator
snippet.description:
Download GooglePlay: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.MalokeGames.WeaponsSimulatorFullPack

The new Weapons Simulator uses an Advanced Bullet Dynamics for simulating the bullet's trajectory. It considers real data like bullet's mass, speed, air drag, barrel length, spindrift, and etc...

On this video, we can see some of these effects while the system was being calibrated.

More Games Here: https://maloke.itch.io/
Play Browser: https://www.kongregate.com/games/Maloke/outdoor-shooting-simulator
